<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style_admin.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <div class="admin-layout">
    <aside class="admin-sidebar">
      <div class="admin-logo">
        <strong>스마트 약상자</strong>
        <span>관리자</span>
      </div>

      <nav class="admin-menu">
        <a href="/admin" class="active">대시보드</a>
        <a href="/admin/members">회원관리</a>
        <a href="/admin/medicine_boxes">약상자 관리</a>
        <a href="/admin/messages">알림 메시지</a>
      </nav>
    </aside>

    <main class="admin-main">
      <header class="admin-header">
        <div>
          <h1>관리자 대시보드</h1>
          <p>스마트 약상자 서비스 현황을 확인할 수 있습니다.</p>
        </div>
          <div class="admin-user-menu">
    <button type="button" class="admin-user-button" id="adminUserButton">
      관리자
      <span>▼</span>
    </button>

    <div class="admin-user-dropdown" id="adminUserDropdown">
      <a href="/admin/profile">개인정보 수정</a>
      <a href="/admin/members_update">회원정보 수정</a>
      <a href="/">로그아웃</a>
    </div>
  </div>


      </header>

      <section class="stats-grid">
        <article class="stat-card">
          <span>전체 회원</span>
          <strong>128</strong>
          <p>등록된 전체 사용자</p>
        </article>

        <article class="stat-card">
          <span>보호자 회원</span>
          <strong>42</strong>
          <p>회원 구분 P</p>
        </article>

        <article class="stat-card">
          <span>시니어 회원</span>
          <strong>76</strong>
          <p>회원 구분 S</p>
        </article>

        <article class="stat-card">
          <span>관리자</span>
          <strong>10</strong>
          <p>회원 구분 A</p>
        </article>
      </section>

      <section class="admin-content">
        <div class="admin-panel">
          <div class="panel-header">
            <h2>최근 가입 회원</h2>
            <button type="button">전체보기</button>
          </div>

          <table class="admin-table">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>아이디</th>
                <th>이름</th>
                <th>회원 구분</th>
                <th>가입일</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td>senior01</td>
                <td>김민수</td>
                <td>S</td>
                <td>2026-06-22</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>parent02</td>
                <td>이지은</td>
                <td>P</td>
                <td>2026-06-22</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>admin01</td>
                <td>관리자</td>
                <td>A</td>
                <td>2026-06-21</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <div class="admin-panel">
          <div class="panel-header">
            <h2>서비스 알림</h2>
          </div>

          <ul class="notice-list">
            <li>
              <strong>알림</strong>
              <span>오늘 확인이 필요한 알림 5건</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>기기 연결 상태</strong>
              <span>오프라인 약상자 2대</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>신규 문의</strong>
              <span>확인 대기 문의 3건</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </div>
  <script>
  const adminUserButton = document.querySelector("#adminUserButton");
  const adminUserDropdown = document.querySelector("#adminUserDropdown");

  adminUserButton.addEventListener("click", () => {
    adminUserDropdown.classList.toggle("show");
  });

  document.addEventListener("click", (event) => {
    const isMenuClick = event.target.closest(".admin-user-menu");

    if (!isMenuClick) {
      adminUserDropdown.classList.remove("show");
    }
  });
</script>


</body>
</html>